  {
   "ruleId": 26642,
   "ruleLevel": 1,
   "title": null,
   "ruleText": "<table style=\"width: 100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15%\" align=\"center\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><b>MUZ-P1</b></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 85%\">\n<p><b>Accommodating growth</b></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Provide for the use and development of the Mixed Use Zone to meet the City’s needs for business activities and to a lesser extent housing, including:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>A variety of <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>building</a> type, size, affordability and distribution, including forms of medium density housing;</li>\n<li>Efficient, well integrated and strategic use of available development sites; and</li>\n<li>Convenient <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>access</a> to state highways and key transport routes.</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
   "ruleComments": null,
   "sectionNumber": null,
   "pcid": 0,
   "finalised": true,
   "ruleFilter": 0,
   "titleSize": 0,
   "ruleTextSize": 5,
   "shading": 0,
   "indent": 0,
   "greyText": 0,
   "greyRefNum": 0,
   "subText": null,
   "tableMerge": true,
   "legalEffect": false,
   "nps": false,
   "olSpacing": false,
   "conseqChange": false,
   "pcReason": null,
   "template": null,
   "compareRule": null,
   "appeals": [],
   "footnotes": []
  },
  {
   "ruleId": 8054,
   "ruleLevel": 1,
   "title": null,
   "ruleText": "<table style=\"width: 100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15%\" align=\"center\">\n<p><b>MUZ-P2</b></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 85%\">\n<p><b>Enabled activities </b></p>\n<p><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\n<p>Enable a wide range of compatible activities in the Mixed Use Zone where they are of an appropriate nature, scale and intensity for the zone and the hierarchy of centres, including:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Commercial activities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Community facilities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Educational facilities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Recreation activities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Arts, culture and entertainment activities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Emergency service facilities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Community corrections activities</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Visitor accommodation</a>;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Residential activities</a> above ground floor level;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Public transport activities</a>;&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Industrial activities</a>;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Carparking activities; and</li>\n<li><a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>Hospital activities</a> and healthcare facilities.</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
   "ruleComments": null,
   "sectionNumber": "<span style=\"color: #843FA1\"><b>Have regard to PC1 amendment</b></span>",
   "pcid": 0,
   "finalised": true,
