  {
   "ruleId": 8055,
   "ruleLevel": 1,
   "title": null,
   "ruleText": "<table style=\"width: 100%\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 15%\" align=\"center\">\n<p><b>MUZ-P3</b></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 85%\">\n<p><b>Managing larger-scale <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>retail activities</a> </b></p>\n<p><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\n<p>Only allow the establishment of <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>integrated retail activities</a> and large supermarkets in the Mixed Use Zone if it can be demonstrated that they will:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Not result in significant adverse impacts on the vitality, role and function of the City Centre or any Metropolitan, Local or Neighbourhood Centres;</li>\n<li>Not result in significant adverse impacts on the sustainability, safety or efficiency of the <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>transport network</a> and the hierarchy of roads from trip patterns, travel demand or <a href='' role='button' class='divRuleTextDef' onruleclick='scrolltoDefinition(event)'>vehicle</a> use; and</li>\n<li>Be compatible with adjoining land uses.</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
